videos.description: Penn State's Trace McSorley gets off to a rough start as he throws an interception to Akron's Zach Guiser in the end zone.
videos.headline: McSorley throws INT in the end zone

videos.description: Penn State's DeAndre Thompkins returns the punt 61 yards for a touchdown, giving the Nittany Lions a lead over Akron.
videos.headline: Penn State takes it to the house on punt return

videos.description: Penn State's Amani Oruwariye leaps into the air to make the diving interception off of Akron's Thomas Woodson.
videos.headline: Penn State makes an athletic INT

videos.description: Penn State's Saquon Barkley hurdles over the defender to get the first down for the Nittany Lions.
videos.headline: Barkley leaps for the 1st down

videos.description: Penn State's Trace McSorley finds Mike Gesicki in the end zone for a 13-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: McSorley TD pass pads Penn State's lead against Akron

videos.description: Penn State's Nittany Lion dances on the field with a couple of mannequins in the rain.
videos.headline: Nittany Lion shows off dance moves

videos.description: Penn State's Saquon Barkley breaks open for an 80-yard run, but steps out of bounds just shy of a touchdown.
videos.headline: Barkley shows off his speed

videos.description: Penn State's Trace McSorley runs into the end zone for the four-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: McSorley keeps it for the TD

videos.description: Penn State's Saquon Barkley waltzes into the end zone for the 3-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Barkley struts into the end zone

videos.description: Penn State's Saquon Barkley turns the corner and motors into the end zone for the 30-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Barkley gets into the end zone for the second time

videos.description: Penn State head coach James Franklin discusses Saquon Barkley's running and his runs that came up just short of the end zone.
videos.headline: James Franklin talks Saquon Barkley's running

videos.description: Penn State's Saquon Barkley reverses the field and powers forward for the 25-yard run.
videos.headline: Barkley makes 'lemonade out of lemons'

videos.description: Penn State's Trace McSorley finds Mike Gesicki in the end zone for their second touchdown of the game.
videos.headline: McSorley and Gesicki connect for the 2nd time

videos.description: Penn State's Tommy Stevens runs for five yards and Akron's Deon'Tae Moore leads with his helmet and is called for targeting, leading to his ejection from the game.
videos.headline: Akron's Moore ejected for targeting

videos.description: Penn State's Tommy Stevens runs into the end zone to give the Nittany Lions the 52-0 lead over Akron.
videos.headline: Penn State scores 52 unanswered points

videos.description: Penn State head coach James Franklin breaks down the production from the dominant offense in Penn State's 52-0 victory over Akron.
videos.headline: James Franklin talks 'offensive weapons'

videos.description: Penn State RB Saquon Barkley discusses playing in Happy Valley for the season opener in Penn State's win over Akron.
videos.headline: Saquon Barkley talks season opening performance

videos.description: Rod Gilmore and Mark Jones break down Penn State's dominant offense in it's 52-0 victory over Akron.
videos.headline: Digging deep with Penn State's strong offense

videos.description: Saquon Barkley dominates with his 5th career game with over 200 yards from scrimmage.
